{"tid":2223417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍MQ-9收割者無人機隊新臂章曝光 中共震驚","createTime":"2020-09-29T22:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:59:04.000Z","uid":337052,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b87f8be24853295303c784b38e8fb960067a8f","tid":2223417,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T22:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.airforcemag.com/app/uploads/2020/09/200915-F-HV115-1841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airforcemag.com%2Fapp%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F200915-F-HV115-1841.jpg&h=f1c3d421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">With an Eye on China, Reaper Drones Train for Maritime War</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.airforcemag.com/with-an-eye-on-china-reaper-drones-train-for-maritime-war/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airforcemag.com%2Fwith-an-eye-on-china-reaper-drones-train-for-maritime-war%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=8c42c7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.airforcemag.com/with-an-eye-on-china-reaper-drones-train-for-maritime-war/</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jF4Wv8fVUu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjF4Wv8fVUu8&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=185b246f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jF4Wv8fVUu8</a><br />\n美軍MQ-9收割者無人機 美軍最新臂章曝光 中南坑那幾個腿都軟了<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Iq21I81ZfIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIq21I81ZfIE&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=360a91b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Iq21I81ZfIE</a><br />\nMQ-9收割者無人機搭配AGM-114R9X飛彈飛彈"},{"pid":"ba05cf58502d886b2e9f0de0a340b54906dc0e16","tid":2223417,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:00:20.000Z","msg":"「射刀片」的飛彈？ 美軍再祭神秘「忍者飛彈」 靠血滴子殲敵<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/27 20:51<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕據《紐約時報》報導，近兩個星期前，美軍特種部隊在敘利亞西北部罕見地動用無人機搭配秘密武器「忍者飛彈」，成功狙殺恐怖組織「開打」（Al-Qaeda）一名高層，這已是近3個月以來，美軍特種部隊第3次以這種特殊設計的飛彈在敘國西北部斬殺恐怖組織首腦。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，這秘密的「忍者」飛彈就是AGM-114R9X飛彈。它是AGM-114「地獄火」（Hellfire）飛彈的秘密新改良型，特殊之處是用6片鋒利刀刃取代傳統彈頭，可由MQ-9「死神」（Reaper）無人機搭載投射，在衝擊前一刻，飛彈上的刀片會亮出並高速旋轉，以冷兵器切割式攻擊目標，殺人方式酷似古代中國傳說的「血滴子」。<br />\n<br />\n「開打」組織領袖看準美軍擔憂以飛彈襲擊容易誤傷平民，因此偏好在敘利亞都會區行動。但改良後的地獄火飛彈不會爆炸，反而會直接以100磅的飛彈衝向目標造成傷害，若攻擊未能奪取敵人性命，飛彈內還有6片刀片會在衝擊前射出，將恐怖份子連人帶車切碎，但是附帶損傷極小，除了對汽車內的乘員造成致命殺傷，周遭的人或者物基本毫髮無損。<br />\n<br />\n當初美軍會發展這款飛彈，是要將平民死傷降到最低，避免因為強力爆炸，導致目標和周遭環境嚴重毀損。不過，它上面的刀刃十分鋒利，能削鐵如泥，穿透建築和車身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/27/3304972_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F3304972_2_1.jpg&h=d4c12ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAGM-114R9X飛彈的利刃可切斷金屬。（示意圖，翻攝自推特/@Charles_Lister）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3304972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3304972&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=dacb129f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3304972&h=1bbb0337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3304972</a>"},{"pid":"42837b7a72f65f62d812952977f1fe1253c9a634","tid":2223417,"uid":273703,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:04:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fa8787e47e19fc0c6df7cf041d8350a9cccb38c","tid":2223417,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:05:34.000Z","msg":"想像唔到<br />\n等睇高手整動畫"},{"pid":"102a2605214710a9dd105e6efdbebcbdf8edfb18","tid":2223417,"uid":17443,"